  plantName: Blanket Flower
  description: "Blanket flower (Gaillardia) is a tough, drought-tolerant, and long-blooming
    perennial wildflower known for its vibrant red, yellow, and orange daisy-like
    flowers. Thriving in full sun and poor soil, these,, popular garden plants grow
    24\u201336 inches tall, flower from summer to fall, and are excellent for attracting
    pollinators while resisting deer."
